data.description: Welcome!!! This is what you've been looking for. A very spacious 5 bedroom & 2.5 bathroom house in Apple Valley CA, with 2,220 sq. foot of living space. Situated on a generous 26,400 sq. ft lot, built in 1984. This was a licensed home care facility before. License has expired. Take advantage of the booming community's amenities. Conveniently located near shopping malls, grocery stores and various amenities. Buyer & Buyer's representatives, please do your due diligence. Sellers acquired this home with 5 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms (buyer to verify).  Leased Solar - with Sunnova. Buyer will take over lease agreement. Or negotiable.  DO NOT GO DIRECT!!! Dogs in the backyard.    *******BACK ON MARKET ************** THIS IS YOUR CHANCE DO NOT MISS OUT THE 2ND TIME! ****
